[
  "Candido Junior is the younger son of Candido Pinheiro Koren de Lima, who founded Brazilian health insurance and hospital firm Hapvida. ",
  "He is Hapvida's commercial and relationship vice president and serves as a board member. ",
  "His older brother Jorge Pinheiro Koren de Lima, also a billionaire, is Hapvida's CEO. ",
  "The family took Hapvida public on the Sao Paulo Stock Exchange in April 2018. His father Candido, the company's chairman, is also a billionaire."
